Achievements.Name: Medal of Honor
Achievements.Description: Complete 1 Mass Effect Playthrough on any setting

Achievements.Name: Long Service Medal
Achievements.Description: Complete 2 Mass Effect Playthroughs on any setting

Achievements.Name: Distinguished Combat Medal
Achievements.Description: Complete 1 Mass Effect playthrough on the Hardcore difficulty setting. Do not change the setting.

Achievements.Name: Medal of Valor
Achievements.Description: Complete 1 Mass Effect playthrough on the Insanity difficulty setting. Do not change the setting.

Achievements.Description: Complete the majority of the game with the Alliance sentinel squad member

Achievements.Name: Krogan Ally
Achievements.Description: Complete the majority of the game with the krogan squad member

Achievements.Name: Turian Ally
Achievements.Description: Complete the majority of the game with the turian squad member

Achievements.Name: Quarian Ally
Achievements.Description: Complete the majority of the game with the quarian squad member

Achievements.Name: Asari Ally
Achievements.Description: Complete the majority of the game with the asari squad member
